            {
                id: "five_steps",
                title: "18. The Five Critical Steps",
                content: `
                    <h1>18. Five Critical Things to Do Immediately</h1>
                    <p>Completing these transforms OpenClaw from a chatbot to an autonomous employee.</p>

                    <h3>18.1 Brain Dump Context</h3>
                    <p>Interests, Career, Goals, Ambitions. (See Section 6.1)</p>

                    <h3>18.2 Connect Tools</h3>
